On today’s episode >>> swipe to see what I saw today 🌳💗🫶🏼

First stop: Chippenham Lacock — where parts of Harry Potter were filmed! So magical to see in real life 🤍
Next up: the stunning Stourhead House & Gardens… seriously, like secret garden meets period drama. 
And finally, of course — Stonehenge 🪨😀
